24	// Auth: Marketify HS256 JWT (MARKETIFY_JWT_SECRET), app_role must be 'lister'.
25	//       Gateway `verify_jwt` is disabled because Supabase-issued JWTs aren't
26	//       the same namespace — the handler enforces auth via _shared/jwt.ts.
